# Instagram Clone
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)


## Description
This a web application built using Python and Django. The app is basically a clone of the awwards app, where a user can post a project for other users to review and rate it. The projects are rated based on design, usability and content. The user can also rate projects posted to the application


## Author

Joshua Kimani

## Link to site


# Installation

## Clone
    
```bash
    git clone https://github.com/JKimani77/awards.git
    
```
##  Create virtual environment
```bash
    python3.6 -m venv --without-pip virtual
    
```
## Activate virtual and install requirements.txt
```bash
   $ source virtual/bin/activate
   $ pip install - requirements.txt
    
```
## Create SQLDatabase and configure settings


## Run initial migration
```bash
   $ python3.6 manage.py makemigrations awards
   $ python3.6 manage.py migrate
    
```


## Run app
```bash
   $ python3 manage.py runserver
    
```

## Test class

```bash
    $ python3 manage.py test
```

